1. *Pevam* pesmu koju sam naučila juče. (I am singing the song that I learned yesterday.)
2. Ja obično *pevam* u horu svake nedelje. (I usually sing in the choir every Sunday.)
3. Oni su nas *pevali* u svim tonovima cele noći. (They sang to us in all tones all night long.)
4. Da li ti *pevaš* dok voziš automobil? (Do you sing while driving a car?)
5. *Pevaću* na prijateljevoj svadbi ovog vikenda. (I will sing at my friend's wedding this weekend.)
6. Nemoj da me *pevaš* sada, već kasnije kada se smirim. (Don't sing to me now, but later when I calm down.)
7. Kada sam bio mali, moja baka bi mi *pevala* uspavanke. (When I was a child, my grandmother would sing lullabies to me.)
8. *Pevajući* pod tušem, zaboravio sam da sam zakasnio na sastanak. (Singing in the shower, I forgot that I was late for the meeting.)
9. Kada *budem pevao* na koncertu, želim da sve bude savršeno. (When I sing at the concert, I want everything to be perfect.)
10. Da li je istina da *si pevao* sinoć u karaoke baru? (Is it true that you sang at the karaoke bar last night?)